rawText:
BABU S R
Address: 1st Stage, Kumaraswamy Layout Bengaluru, Karnataka 560078, India
Mobile Number: 6360328864
Email: babusrofficial@gmail.com
Summary:
Motivated Laravel developer with Eight Months of experience in designing, developing,
and maintaining web applications. Proficient in PHP, MySQL, JavaScript, HTML, and
CSS. Ability to work in a team environment and meet tight deadlines.
Professional Experience:
Laravel Developer
Company Name: Web Digital Mantra It Services Limited
Location: #23, 3rd floor, nandita manison, 1st Cross, 1st Stage, Kumaraswamy Layout, Bengaluru,
Karnataka 560078
Duration: Oct 1st 2022 to Present (8 Months)
Designed and developed web applications using Laravel PHP framework, HTML, CSS, and
JavaScript.
Worked on the development of the front-end and back-end of web applications.
Created responsive designs that are optimized for desktop and mobile devices.
Developed and maintained APIs for mobile and web applications.
Worked with Git and version control to manage source code changes.
Utilized MySQL to manage databases and performed data migrations.
Collaborated with team members to develop efficient solutions for complex issues.
Conducted code reviews and provided feedback to ensure the quality of code.
Skills:
Laravel PHP framework
MySQL
HTML

CSS
JavaScript
Git
API Development
Ajax
Education:
Bachelor's Degree in Science (PCM)
University Name: University College of Science Tumkur
Location: Tumkur
Graduation Year: 2018
Projects:
Developed an e-commerce website using Laravel, allowing customers to browse and purchase
products securely. Implemented features like user registration, product search, shopping cart,
and payment integration.
Created a matrimony platform using Laravel, enabling users to create profiles, search for
potential partners, and communicate securely. Implemented advanced search filters, matching
algorithms, and privacy settings.
Built a tours and travels website similar to MakeMyTrip using Laravel, providing users with the
ability to search and book flights, hotels, and holiday packages. Implemented dynamic pricing,
booking management, and integrated third-party APIs.
Developed an informative dynamic website using Laravel, allowing users to browse and search
for articles, news, and resources. Implemented a content management system (CMS) for easy
content updates.
Created a temple poojas project using Laravel, where each pooja has different packages based
on package prices. Implemented features such as package selection, payment integration, and
booking management.
